des:
Famously hilarious and "comedically humorous" quotes by one of the greatest TV characters - Michael Scott, from one of the greatest TV shows - The Office. You can now hear them in Alexa's voice!
This is a compilation of some of the gems from Michael!
New speech synthesis enabled quotes to be added in every update!
